```
static volatile int count = 0;

void increment() {
    count++;
}
```

```
Thread t1 = new Thread(new Runnable() {
    @Override
    public void run() {
        for(int index=0; index<1000; index++) {
            increment();
        }
    }
});

Thread t2 = new Thread(new Runnable() {
    @Override
    public void run() {
        for(int index=0; index<1000; index++) {
            increment();
        }
    }
});

t1.start();
t2.start();

t1.join();
t2.join();
```
